citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:25pm on
29-Jan-20.
The inspector arrived at the facility at 2:25pm and knocked on the door, called all the phone numbers and left
messages. The inspector waited 30 minutes and then left the facility.
